  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.awt.event.ActionListener, java.awt.event.ItemListener, java.awt.image.ImageObserver, java.awt.MenuContainer, java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Runnable, java.util.EventListener, javax.accessibility.Accessible, javax.swing.RootPaneContainer, javax.swing.WindowConstants

    public class GammaBetaFrame
extends javax.swing.JFrame
implements java.awt.event.ActionListener, java.awt.event.ItemListener, java.lang.Runnable
    Main class for computing detector efficiency by Monte Carlo method using EGSnrc engine or Geant4 engine! It is also used for computing dose, fluence and stopping power in RZ geometry. Basically, it is GUI interface for GammaDetEffA, GammaDetA, SpwrRz, FluenceEz and BremsApp2.
    Author:
    Dan Fulea, 11 Jul. 2005
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
